---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
import siteConfig from '@/site-config'
---

<BaseLayout description={siteConfig.description}>
  <article class="prose">
    <div class="flex flex-col-reverse md:flex-row gap-8 items-start mb-8">
      <div class="flex-1">
        <h1 class="text-title mb-2">Alex Gurung</h1>
        <p class="text-xl opacity-75 italic mt-0 mb-6">Bridging Human Behavior & Digital Interfaces.</p>

        <p>
          I am a <b>Graduate Research Assistant</b> at the University of Michigan specializing in Human-Computer Interaction
          and Applied AI. My work blends <b>Human Centered AI Research</b> with <b>Front End Development</b> to engineer
          intelligent systems that prioritize the human experience.
        </p>

        <p>
          Beyond my work, I’m fueled by mountain hikes, spontaneous travel plans, and discovering the best local eats,
          occasionally share my food explorations on my food channel.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-6">
          <a
            href="/resume.pdf"
            target="_blank"
            class="no-underline inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-2 bg-white !text-black rounded-full font-mono font-bold hover:bg-gray-200 transition-colors shadow-lg border border-transparent"
          >
            <span class="i-carbon-document-download text-xl"></span> Download Resume
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex-shrink-0 mx-auto md:mx-0">
        <img
          src="/hero.jpg"
          alt="Alex Gurung"
          class="w-48 h-48 md:w-56 md:h-56 object-cover rounded-2xl shadow-xl rotate-3 hover:rotate-0 transition-all duration-300"
        />
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="my-8 border-l-4 border-gray-500 pl-4 italic bg-zinc-900/30 p-4 rounded-r-lg">
      <p class="m-0">
        <b>First Author:</b> IEEE FIE 2025 Conference<br />
        <b>Photography:</b> 5M+ Downloads on Unsplash<br />
        <b>Engineering:</b> Built EHR systems for 10+ hospitals
      </p>
    </div>
    <hr class="hr-line" />

    <section class="mt-12 mb-12">
      <div class="flex justify-between items-end mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white m-0">Featured Projects</h2>
        <a href="/projects" class="text-sm text-blue-400 no-underline hover:underline">View All Projects →</a>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <a
          href="/projects"
          class="group block bg-zinc-900/40 border border-zinc-800 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden hover:border-zinc-700 transition-all no-underline"
        >
          <div class="aspect-video w-full bg-zinc-800 relative overflow-hidden">
            <img
              src="/public/smart-glasses.jpg"
              alt="Smart Glass Preview"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500"
            />
            <span
              class="absolute top-3 left-3 bg-blue-600/80 text-white text-[10px] font-bold px-2 py-1 rounded uppercase tracking-wider backdrop-blur-sm"
              >HCI Research</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="p-5">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white m-0 group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">
              Smart Glass for Low Vision
            </h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-2 line-clamp-2">
              AR & Audio interaction patterns for AI wearables to reduce cognitive load.
            </p>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a
          href="/projects"
          class="group block bg-zinc-900/40 border border-zinc-800 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden hover:border-zinc-700 transition-all no-underline"
        >
          <div class="aspect-video w-full bg-zinc-800 relative overflow-hidden">
            <img
              src="/public/hospital22.gif"
              alt="ML Dashboard Preview"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500"
            />
            <span
              class="absolute top-3 left-3 bg-emerald-600/80 text-white text-[10px] font-bold px-2 py-1 rounded uppercase tracking-wider backdrop-blur-sm"
              >Applied AI</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="p-5">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white m-0 group-hover:text-emerald-400 transition-colors">
              Healthcare Readmission ML
            </h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-2 line-clamp-2">
              Interpretable ML models built with SHAP to understand 30-day hospital risk factors.
            </p>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
    <hr class="hr-line" />

    <p>Connect with me:</p>
    <div class="flex gap-4">
      <a
        href="https://github.com/alexgurung"
        target="_blank"
        class="no-underline hover:text-blue-500 font-bold flex items-center gap-2"
      >
        <span class="i-simple-icons-github"></span> GitHub
      </a>
      <span>/</span>
      <a
        href="https://unsplash.com/@alexgurung"
        target="_blank"
        class="no-underline hover:text-blue-500 font-bold flex items-center gap-2"
      >
        <span class="i-simple-icons-unsplash"></span> Unsplash
      </a>
      <span>/</span>
      <a
        href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/alexgurung10"
        target="_blank"
        class="no-underline hover:text-blue-500 font-bold flex items-center gap-2"
      >
        <span class="i-simple-icons-linkedin"></span> LinkedIn
      </a>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
